source.name: Office of Adoption and Child Custody Advocacy - Performance Measures - Fingerprints Clearance 2009
source.description: When an individual or family wish to adopt, they must obtain a fingerprint clearance.  This Office is the pass through agency for the FBI, Illinois State Police, and the courts
